java.io.Serializable
class ShibbolethAuthenticationToken
extends org.springframework.security.authentication.AbstractAuthenticationToken

An Authentication object needed to load the ShibbolethUserDetailsService with the native Shibboleth SP (Service Provider). This ShibbolethAuthenticationToken is capable of loading an Authentication from an eppn provided by the shibboleth native SP.

Authors:
Aaron J. Zirbes

Field Detail

DEFAULT_AUTHORITIES

private static final java.util.List DEFAULT_AUTHORITIES
Some Spring Security classes (e.g. RoleHierarchyVoter) expect at least one role, so we give a user with no granted roles this one which gets past that restriction but doesn't grant anything.
